This section covers all aspects of non-graphics OpenTTD development. For those new to development, the [[en/Development/FAQ development|FAQ]] should answer any questions you have.  You can then move on to current [[en/Development/Main Page]] or helping out with [[en/Archive/Community/Internationalization|translation]] if you wish. 

You can see the [[en/Recent and Current Developments|latest developments]], [[en/Archive/Lists/Roadmap|expected features for the upcoming releases]] and the [[en/Archive/Community/Requested features]] list if you're interested in the current state of the project. If you're already a developer, the [[en/Development/Main Page]] is useful.

We also have a development community on our [[en/Development/IRC channel]] and in the [http://www.tt-forums.net/viewforum.php?f=33 development forum].
